<h2>Change Password</h2>

<p>You can change your account's password.</p>
<br />

<p>Step 1: Once you log in, go to "Manage your Account" page by clicking on your email on the header.</p>
<img src="~/images/details.png" style="height:400px" />

<br />
<br />
<br />

<p>Step 2: Click on the "Settings" tab.</p>
<img src="~/images/settings.png" style="height:400px" />

<br />
<br />
<br />

<p>Step 3: Click "Change Password" button.</p>
<p>A form to change password will appear.</p>
<img src="~/images/change_password.png" style="height:400px" />

<br />
<br />
<br />

<p>Step 4: Fill out the form with new password then click on "Update password" button.</p>
<p>Password will be successfullly changed.</p>
<img src="~/images/password_changed.png" style="height:400px" />

